title: Dakota Pipeline Protest Camp Set On Fire After Order To Evacuate Area - BuzzFeed News
text: Campers set structures on fire in preparation of the Army Corp’s 2pm deadline to leave the Oceti Sakowin protest camp, Feb. 22, 2017 in Cannon Ball, North Dakota.
